OK let me get this straight.  I'm out soloing in RvR.  I mez a target and do 1 point of damage.  I don't do anything else to the target.  A scout then attacks the target and kills him without getting help from someone else.  Does that mean the scout and I split the RPs 50/50?  That doesn't sound right.  I've always been under the impression RPs were gained based on how much damage you inflict.  How would doing 1 point of damage when mezzing improve our ability to gain RPs?<P>Galtin
