<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">
They would not be immune to mez. the mez would stick and they would drop any chants. Notice, chants do not break Mez anyway, only direct heals.<P>And I never said they take 1 point of damage, I said they should lose 1 HP. The change in HP should be enough to get an RP split and allow the heal to break it. It may have to be more like 5 or so.<P>As for the RP split. It is supposed to be not based on damage done. Groups get a bonus, and then an even split. Everyone gets an even split of the total. So if we mez and a group kills, do we get 1/2, then they get the other half with a gorup bonus and an even split?<P>Who the hell knows for sure...<P>All I know is this. We are being hammered for having this one ability. This one ability can single handedly sway a battle. We are target numero uno because of this dreaded ability. And right now it earns us NO RPs.<P>I would rather see 1 RP per target than Zero. So I am not sure how this would split, but ANY split is better than what we have now.<P>--------------------<P>i3ullseye<BR>"You're good, but me? I'm Magic!"<P>Rictus -Sorceror(DAOC)/Rictus(EQ)<BR>DAOC Sorceror team lead...<P>Please visit our <A HREF="http://www.yesterdayland.com/popopedia/shows/toys/ty1050.php" TARGET=_blank>Sponsors!</A>  <IMG SRC="biggrin.gif" border="0">
